      },
      "date": "2013-01-07 17:38:56.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nIsn't this the same as my patch http://review.whamcloud.com/4682? It did the same - move ROOT fid to FID_SEQ_SPECIAL and other things.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 6
